    "description": "Omkar Realtors South Asia Partners, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Real Estate Agent for our Srinagar operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Omkar Realtors South Asia Partners:\nOmkar Realtors South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Omkar Realtors South Asia Partners!",
